  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "This ERC proposes a specification for an opaque token that enhances privacy by concealing balance information. Privacy is achieved by representing balances as off-chain data encapsulated in hashes, referred to as \"baskets\". These baskets can be reorganized, transferred, and managed through token functions on-chain.",
  "title": "Opaque Token"
